    "description": "Crescent Cauldron Café is a casual co-op management game where you play as two sisters running their family's café. Both sisters are witches of a different variety and use their abilities for different roles.<br><br>Sage manages the storefront - Baking bread, preparing coffee, and mixing potions. Mercury isn't interested in any of that, but does want to fly around on her broom to deliver orders.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Asymmetrical local co-op<br></li><li> Fly around on a broom as Mercury. Finding faster routes means getting deliveries knocked out quicker<br></li><li> Manage the storefront and oncoming customers as Sage, while prepping items for Mercury to deliver<br></li><li> Purchase upgrades for each sister and the store</li></ul><br>An additional gamepad is required to play local co-op. Crescent Cauldron Café can also be played solo, which allows you to switch between sisters.",
